1. Description
--------------
pyDKB testing stage.

Run as:

  ./json2TTL.py -i input
  ./json2TTL.py input/196.json
  cat << EOF | ./json2TTL.py -m s | less
  {"a": 1}
  {"b": 2}
  EOF
  ./json2TTL.py --hdfs -i /my/test/input

etc

2. What to check
----------------

Test cases:

(+) in file mode with no parameters
    (expected: "no input file specified" error):

  ./json2TTL.py -m f

(+) without parameters
    (expeted: same as in file mode without parameters)

  ./json2TTL.py

(+) read input from file(s)
(+) output to (s)tream
    (expected: output file(s) content)

  ./json2TTL.py -d s input/NDjson.json
  ./json2TTL.py -d s input/NDjson.json input/NDjson.json
